## debugFlags variable

Flags that can be stripped by dead code removal tools. Shouldn't be used in production.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
debugFlags: {
    DEBUG_MODE_FLAG: "DEBUG_MODE";
    DEBUG_DISABLE_BREAKPOINT_FLAG: "DEBUG_DISABLE_BREAKPOINT";
}
```
